[
    {
        "text": "Fair trade aims to establish equitable conditions of trade and commerce...",
        "startTime": 2110,
        "endTime": 5509,
        "slowStartTime": 3315,
        "slowEndTime": 8489
    },
    {
        "text": "...between countries in the north and the south.",
        "startTime": 5591,
        "endTime": 7311,
        "slowStartTime": 8537,
        "slowEndTime": 11191
    },
    {
        "text": "The concept appeared after the Second World War,...",
        "startTime": 7777,
        "endTime": 9833,
        "slowStartTime": 11816,
        "slowEndTime": 14974
    },
    {
        "text": "...and received its first certification in 1988 in Mexico.",
        "startTime": 10026,
        "endTime": 14125,
        "slowStartTime": 15189,
        "slowEndTime": 21412
    },
    {
        "text": "A cooperative of small coffee producers of the state of Oaxaca...",
        "startTime": 14405,
        "endTime": 17855,
        "slowStartTime": 21757,
        "slowEndTime": 27007
    },
    {
        "text": "...partnered with the Dutch NGO to create the Max Havelaar label,...",
        "startTime": 18186,
        "endTime": 21833,
        "slowStartTime": 27429,
        "slowEndTime": 32975
    },
    {
        "text": "...named after a hero of a Dutch novel.",
        "startTime": 22067,
        "endTime": 24371,
        "slowStartTime": 33250,
        "slowEndTime": 36781
    },
    {
        "text": "The principle was simple:",
        "startTime": 24839,
        "endTime": 25961,
        "slowStartTime": 37408,
        "slowEndTime": 39166
    },
    {
        "text": "The NGO buys the coffee at a fixed price...",
        "startTime": 26316,
        "endTime": 28971,
        "slowStartTime": 39624,
        "slowEndTime": 43681
    },
    {
        "text": "...and the farmers, unaffected by the fluctuations of the market,...",
        "startTime": 29038,
        "endTime": 32205,
        "slowStartTime": 43707,
        "slowEndTime": 48532
    },
    {
        "text": "...can then live off their work.",
        "startTime": 32467,
        "endTime": 34151,
        "slowStartTime": 48851,
        "slowEndTime": 51452
    },
    {
        "text": "A part of the money is then used to finance schools and health centers.",
        "startTime": 34705,
        "endTime": 38419,
        "slowStartTime": 52207,
        "slowEndTime": 57854
    },
    {
        "text": "By eliminating middlemen, distribution costs are also reduced.",
        "startTime": 38832,
        "endTime": 42621,
        "slowStartTime": 58398,
        "slowEndTime": 64156
    },
    {
        "text": "The idea is also to supply good quality products while respecting the environment.",
        "startTime": 42819,
        "endTime": 47437,
        "slowStartTime": 64378,
        "slowEndTime": 71380
    },
    {
        "text": "To begin with, fair trade only dealt with a few products:...",
        "startTime": 47965,
        "endTime": 50701,
        "slowStartTime": 72098,
        "slowEndTime": 76277
    },
    {
        "text": "...coffee, bananas, tea and sugar.",
        "startTime": 50862,
        "endTime": 52855,
        "slowStartTime": 76443,
        "slowEndTime": 79508
    },
    {
        "text": "Today, there are fair trade clothes, sneakers and even a smartphone:",
        "startTime": 53613,
        "endTime": 57712,
        "slowStartTime": 80570,
        "slowEndTime": 86793
    },
    {
        "text": "in total, more than 30,000 products.",
        "startTime": 57902,
        "endTime": 60453,
        "slowStartTime": 87003,
        "slowEndTime": 90904
    },
    {
        "text": "Various businesses have also become interested in the idea of fair trade.",
        "startTime": 61015,
        "endTime": 64928,
        "slowStartTime": 91672,
        "slowEndTime": 97617
    },
    {
        "text": "In 2012, the sales of fair trade products were worth 4.8 billion euros...",
        "startTime": 65273,
        "endTime": 70548,
        "slowStartTime": 98060,
        "slowEndTime": 106047
    },
    {
        "text": "...with 1.3 million producers and workers benefiting in 70 countries.",
        "startTime": 70835,
        "endTime": 75987,
        "slowStartTime": 106403,
        "slowEndTime": 114205
    },
    {
        "text": "But the practice also attracts criticism:...",
        "startTime": 76403,
        "endTime": 78631,
        "slowStartTime": 114754,
        "slowEndTime": 118171
    },
    {
        "text": "...the lack of transparency of labels which keep multiplying,...",
        "startTime": 78791,
        "endTime": 81345,
        "slowStartTime": 118337,
        "slowEndTime": 122243
    },
    {
        "text": "...high prices or distributors who increase their margins on products that are in demand.",
        "startTime": 81628,
        "endTime": 86407,
        "slowStartTime": 122592,
        "slowEndTime": 129836
    }
]